PR #27570: Improve overlap percent estimation for low-density ranges in StatisticRange
Changed files (4): core/trino-main/src/main/java/io/trino/cost/StatisticRange.java, core/trino-main/src/test/java/io/trino/cost/TestFilterStatsCalculator.java, core/trino-main/src/test/java/io/trino/cost/TestStatisticRange.java, testing/trino-tests/src/test/resources/sql/trino/tpcds/iceberg/partitioned/q84.plan.txt
